rows.name:
Hello friends! Foorara was reflecting
on bitterness of existence.

rows.label: qst500204_msg0002
rows.name:
People of Invidia and Superbia
seems to like doing wars.

rows.label: qst500204_msg0003
rows.name:
Nopon not do wars really, but world
of merchants fraught with competition.

rows.label: qst500204_msg0004
rows.name:
Peace means no winners or losers,
but life always have winners, so people
must trying to not lose.

rows.label: qst500204_msg0006
rows.name:
Voltis Trade Guild Walky-Walky
Guide Book say, conflict is source
of opportunity.

rows.label: qst500204_msg0007
rows.name:
Foorara brought many Fusty Fungus,
so maybe try selling to Invidia army
to get moneys for travel.

rows.label: qst500204_msg0008
rows.name:
Anyway, maybe we meet again.
Best of luck!
